en: Please ensure the username and password are correct
zh: 請確認用戶名和密碼輸入無誤
cmn: 请确认用户名和密码输入无误

en: Chapter 2: It’s better to make money directly
zh: 第二章:賺錢還是直接點好
cmn: 第二章：赚钱还是直接点好

en: Chapter 3: It’s better to be civilized when making money
zh: 第三章:賺錢還是文明點好
cmn: 第三章：赚钱还是文明点好

en: It’s better to be more practical when making money
It’s better to make money directly
It’s better to be civilized when making money
Please check if the recipient is correctly input and you have enough money.
zh: 請確保收件人名稱正確且你有足夠代幣
cmn: 请确保收件人名称正确且你有足够代币

en: Last game session has not ended or server busy. Please try again later
zh: 上一場游戲尚未結束，或是伺服器繁忙，請稍後再試
cmn: 上一场游戏尚未结束，或是伺服器繁忙，请稍后再试

en: finish chapter 2 while holding $100 to unlock
zh: 完成第二章並持有$100以解鎖
cmn: 完成第二章并持有$100以解锁

en: The most he ever had was: $

zh: 正在匹配其他玩家，如要放棄等待，請按離開大廳
cmn: 正在匹配其他玩家，如要放弃等待，请按离开大厅

en: Slash others to get their money
zh: 砍其他玩家以搶他們的金錢
cmn: 砍其他玩家以抢他们的金钱

en: The last cup noodles were eaten so quickly
zh: 最後的杯面，這麼快就被吃完了
cmn: 最后的杯面，这么快就被吃完了

en: Tomorrow is the day to pay the rent.
zh: 明天就是交房租的日子了
cmn: 明天就是交房租的日子了

en: But my savings have been used up
zh: 然而我的積蓄已經用完了
cmn: 然而我的积蓄已经用完了

en: It seems that I can’t escape the fate of working
zh: 看來我也逃不過打工的命運啊
cmn: 看来我也逃不过打工的命运啊

en: Business has been bad recently. I can only send you 8 dollars today. Please work with the company to tide over this difficult time.
zh: 最近生意不好,今天只能發8塊錢,請與公司共渡時艱
cmn: 最近生意不好，今天只能发8块钱，请与公司共渡时艰

en: This 9 dollar is your salary, take it.
zh: 這9塊錢是你的工資,你拿去吧
cmn: 这9块钱是你的工资，你拿去吧

en: Don't say I treated you badly, just take the 10 dollars.
zh: 別說我虧待你,這10塊錢你拿去吧
cmn: 别说我亏待你，这10块钱你拿去吧

en: Don't think that I will forget that you have already received your salary. I will not pay you twice a day.
zh: 別以為我會忘了你已經拿過工資了,我是不會一天給你發兩次工資的
cmn: 别以为我会忘了你已经拿过工资了，我是不会一天给你发两次工资的

en: Oops! My boss caught me sleeping
zh: 糟了！被老闆看到我睡覺
cmn: 糟了！被老板看到我睡觉

en: I don't know what he will do
Sigh. It’s really miserable to work
Obviously if I take a nap, it won't affect my work
zh: 明明我睡個覺並不影響工作
cmn: 明明我睡个觉并不影响工作

en: But I can’t sleep because my boss doesn’t like it
zh: 卻因為老闆不喜歡而不能睡
cmn: 却因为老板不喜欢而不能睡

en: I really don’t want to stay in this depressing environment for a moment.
zh: 這種壓抑的環境我真的一刻都不想呆
cmn: 这种压抑的环境我真的一刻都不想待

en: The saddest thing is that I still need to work for a long time
zh: 最可悲的是我還需要打很長時間的工
cmn: 最可悲的是我还需要打很长时间的工

en: Doing things you don’t want to do
zh: 做著自己不想做的東西
cmn: 做着自己不想做的东西

en: But it cannot be exchanged for equivalent rewards.
How do I get out of work?
zh: 我又怎麼擺脫工作制度呢
cmn: 我又怎么摆脱工作制度呢

en: There have been many stabbings recently
zh: 最近發生不少砍人事件
cmn: 最近发生不少砍人事件

en: I wonder if they couldn’t bear the pressure of work and went crazy.
zh: 不知道他們是不是承受不住打工的壓力而瘋了呢
cmn: 不知道他们是不是承受不住打工的压力而疯了呢

en: You can’t make much money by working anyway.
zh: 反正打工也賺不了多少錢
cmn: 反正打工也赚不了多少钱

en: I think making money by stabbing isn't a bad idea
zh: 靠砍人賺錢好像做得過喔
cmn: 靠砍人赚钱好像做得过喔

en: I'm going to make a fortune
(After saying that, I picked up my backpack and left)
(Everyone looked at my back and were stunned)
(When I got to the door, the boss stopped me)
No one will dare to hire you then
Anyway, I'm just here to help you defraud other people's money.
zh: 反正在這裏不過是幫你騙別人的錢
cmn: 反正在这里不过是帮你骗别人的钱

en: Then why don't I grab it myself?
I bought all the kitchen knives
I just sharpened the knife in the company toilet
zh: 剛剛就在公司廁所磨好刀
cmn: 刚刚就在公司厕所磨好刀

en: If any of you want to stop me
Come find me on the street!
Hey, did I fall asleep again?
Freud believed that dreams are manifestations of inner desires
zh: 佛洛伊德認為夢是内心欲望的體現
cmn: 弗洛伊德认为梦是内心欲望的体现

en: It seems that I really don’t want to go to work.
zh: 看來我真的很不想上班啊
cmn: 看来我真的很不想上班啊

en: However, it is always not feasible to steal money by killing people.
zh: 不過透過砍人搶錢始終不太可行
cmn: 不过透过砍人抢钱始终不太可行

en: First, it is illegal to kill someone
The legal liability will only be higher than the money stolen.
zh: 法律責任比起搶到的錢只會更高
cmn: 法律责任比起抢到的钱只会更高

en: There is no way I can kill so many people.
zh: 根本沒能力砍過那麼多人
cmn: 根本没能力砍过那么多人

en: Third, I am not a cruel person
My conscience won't feel good either
I'd better think of other ways to make money.
zh: 我還是想其他方法賺錢吧
cmn: 我还是想其他方法赚钱吧

en: Get 200 points in the last game to unlock this level
zh: 在上一關裏獲得200分以解鎖
cmn: 在上一关里获得200分以解锁

en: Press 3 Times to DELETE Your Account
Get 40 points in Pong to unlock this level
zh: 在上一關裏過得40分以解鎖
cmn: 在上一关里获得40分以解锁
